    <div class="card">
      <div class="step-dots" id="a1-dots"><div class="step-dot active"></div><div class="step-dot "></div><div class="step-dot "></div><span style="margin-left:6px; font-size:0.82em; color:#666; font-weight:600;">Clue 1 of 3</span></div>
      <p style="font-size:0.97em; color:#444; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:14px;">Read the clues. Use them to predict which station you've arrived at! 🗺️</p>
      <div id="a1-clues"><div class="clue-box"><div class="clue-label">Clue 1</div>🧙 A very famous fictional wizard catches his train from a secret, magical platform at this station — you'll need to run straight at a solid brick wall to get there!</div></div>
